The 40 years’ reunion of Lagos Secondary Commercial Academy, 1979 Commercial set, will hold on Saturday, June 29.
According to a statement jointly signed by the Chairman of the Planning Committee, Ebenezer Sobowale and the Secretary, Folorunso Hunga, the celebration will be marked with an anniversary ‘get-together’ for all members of the 1979 Commercial set at Agbayewa Memorial College Hall, Obanikro, Lagos at 11a,m.
The purpose for the reunion get-together, according to the statement, is to give back to the school whose products are doing exceedingly well in their various fields of endeavour.
Dignitaries from all over Nigeria and beyond as well as old boys of the college, friends and associates are expected at the event.